Single-database Alembic configuration.

PHN-V2 app code uses raw psycopg SQL and Pydantic models, not
SQLAlchemy ORM models. Alembic still uses SQLAlchemy internally to run
migrations, but there is no ORM metadata target.

Migrations live in `versions/`. Generate a new manual revision with:

    cd backend && uv run alembic revision -m "describe the change"

Apply with:

    cd backend && uv run alembic upgrade head
